# Email Configuration
EMAIL_USER=your-gmail@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password
BUSINESS_EMAIL=your-business-email@gmail.com

# Instructions:
# 1. Replace EMAIL_USER with your Gmail address
# 2. Replace EMAIL_PASS with your Gmail App Password (not regular password)
# 3. Replace BUSINESS_EMAIL with the email where you want to receive bookings
# 4. Rename this file to .env
# 5. Add .env to your .gitignore file

# To generate Gmail App Password:
# 1. Go to Google Account settings
# 2. Enable 2-Factor Authentication
# 3. Go to Security > App passwords
# 4. Generate a new app password for "Mail"
# 5. Use that 16-character password as EMAIL_PASS